---
title: Easy Peasy BBQ Chicken Bites & Avo Tacos with Charred Corn & Sour Cream
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Welcome to the American South, where the barbecue is famous and plentiful! Try this succulent, tangy chicken to see what all the hype is about. Enjoy with a good dollop of sour cream packed in to warm tacos for a Tex-Mex twist on the all-American fare.
